data.description: Welcome to this delightful 4-bedroom, 2 1/4-bathroom tri-level home in Westminster's Stratford Lakes community. Upon entry, you're greeted by a tastefully refreshed interior, highlighting a newly updated kitchen with modern cabinets, stylish backsplash, and tasteful light fixtures, seamlessly connecting to the main living room space. The lower level offers versatility with a dining room or flex space, alongside a spacious bedroom ideal for an office. Upstairs, discover the primary bedroom, an additional bedroom, and bathroom, while the basement provides a welcoming 4th bedroom, perfect for guests. Throughout the home, added storage solutions and a new outdoor shed ensure organization and convenience. Noteworthy features include newer HVAC and furnace systems installed just a few years ago. Outside, enjoy the well-positioned lot with ample backyard space for entertaining, featuring a newly paved patio. Residents relish in community amenities such as walking trails, a pool, and tennis courts nearby. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Stratford Lakes residence your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience comfort, convenience, and community living!
